title: Can't find out what my mystery gift is
body: Hello, I can't figure out what my mystery gift is, can anyone help me? I clicked the box away to fast when it came up and said mystery gift, i got the icon though. Can anyone help me figure out what I got? I looked through all my skins and checked the history of gifting and purchase. Thanks!

replies.body: It looks like so far you've only received the anniversary icon.  There are a lot of accounts to gift so you won't get everything all at once.  Stay up to date at our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-), and hang tight until all of this is wrapped up.  Let me know if you have any questions!
